02:04.990 --> 02:13.984
I have so many questions, one of the things that I want to ask him, what was it like to go into heaven?

02:15.847 --> 02:20.594
And I just started imagining these things and I'm just imagining him

02:20.802 --> 02:23.105
in line at the poorly gates, right?

02:23.145 --> 02:28.091
