02:48.866 --> 02:51.309
Well, you probably know a little bit of doctrine, right?

02:52.611 --> 02:54.293
No, I don't know what that is either.

02:55.555 --> 02:59.801
Oh, okay, well, you're probably good in helping people.

03:01.503 --> 03:03.446
No, I actually robbed people.

03:05.428 --> 03:07.872
