So next thing you know, we have science.

19:17.312 --> 19:22.600
We have helicopters, fire engines, Michael like this.

19:23.121 --> 19:26.546
So the ladder comes up, firemen goes to my car,

19:27.106 --> 19:30.810
The first thing I told the fireman said, hey Chief, thanks for coming.

19:30.850 --> 19:31.311
You know what?

19:31.711 --> 19:36.436
You need to take her first because I believe she has a medical condition.

19:36.516 --> 19:38.018
She's been passing in and out.

19:38.979 --> 19:39.820
Her purse is over there.

19:39.840 --> 19:40.581
